name: Ancient-customs Style
description:
更新了一小下下：

Update two version：

Highface-一个风格化更高，但是绑定了一个京剧脸的版本

  1. 最好把权重设置在0.75-0.85。

    It's best to set the weight between 0.75-0.85.

  2. 可以尝试不同的采样器也许有不同的效果。

    Trying different samplers may have different results.


喜欢的话😊👍♥哦

Q：347200557

A version that is stylized to a higher degree, but bound to a specific facial structure.

Lowface-一个比较灵活，可以更换人物但是风格化较低的版本

A version that is more flexible, allowing for the swapping of characters, but with lower stylization

modelVersions.name: v1.0Highface
modelVersions.description:
Update 2 version：

  1. ‘Highface’ -Theis version had a more distinct style and was also associated with a facial shape.

  2. ‘Lowface’Theis version had a more distinct style and was also associated with a facial shape.-This version has greater flexibility, but the stylization is relatively weaker."

  3. It's best to set the weight around 0.75-0.85.

  4. Trying different samplers can have different effects.

Any questions or need Training set to Q:347200557 ^.^
